entries.title_d: Apparently the Blacklight pirates base their operation out of the Endor system. The coordinates we got from the Blacklight pirate in your last mission weren't exactly accurate though but we have set up a search grid for you to follow and scan.
entries.title: Endor system: The search for the Blacklight base of operations.
entries.split_quest_alert: Brother Ezkiel: < Look out! Keep on the alert, pilot! Blacklights coming in hard and fast! >
entries.quest_patrol_d: We will be updating your nav computer with the search grid we planned out. Stay alert and on the look out for anything suspicious.
entries.quest_location_d: We don't have that much information about the Endor system but the Imperial presence seem unusually high for what seem to be a system with no real value. Be careful out there my friend.
